      • areCustomContentsTheSame

        protected boolean areCustomContentsTheSame(QMUISection<H,T> oldSection,
                                           int oldItemIndex,
                                           QMUISection<H,T> newSection,
                                           int newItemIndex)
        Subclasses overrides this method to check whether two custom items have the same data
        参数:
        oldSection - the old section in the old list
        oldItemIndex - the old item index in old section
        newSection - the new section in the new list
        newItemIndex - the new item index in new section
        返回:
        True if the contents of the items are the same or false if they are different.
